{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.playbackRate","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>playbackRate</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>La propiedad <code><strong>Animation</strong></code><strong><code>.playbackRate</code></strong> de la <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a> devuelve o&nbsp; establece la velocidad de reproducción de la animación.</p>\n\n<p>Las animaciones tienen un <strong>playback rate</strong> que proporciona un factor de escala para el cambio de velocidad de la animación <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> valores del estado actual de la linea de tiempo de la animación. La velocidad de reproducción inicial es <code>1</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">var <em>currentPlaybackRate</em> = <em>Animation</em>.playbackRate;\n\n<em>Animation</em>.playbackRate = <em>newRate</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>Toma un número que puede ser 0, negativo o positivo.</span> <span>Los valores negativos invierten la animación.</span> <span>El valor es un factor de escala, por lo que, por ejemplo, un valor de 2 duplicaría la velocidad de reproducción.</span></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p>si establecemos el <code>playbackRate</code> a <code>0</code> pausa la animación de manera efectiva (sin embargo, su <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\" title=\"playstate\"><code>playstate</code></a> no se convierte necesariamente en&nbsp; <code>paused</code>).</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En el ejemplo <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/PNYGZQ?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Growing/Shrinking Alice Game</a> , hacer click o tocar la botella, hace que la animación de crecimiento de Alicia&nbsp; (<code>aliceChange</code>) se invierta para reducirse:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">shrinkAlice</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playbackRate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Con un toque o un click, Alicia se encogerá.</span>\nbottle<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mousedown\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> shrinkAlice<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nbottle<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"touchstart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> shrinkAlice<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Por el contrario, hacer click en el pastel hace que \"crezca\" reproduciendo <code>aliceChange</code> hacia adelante otra vez:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">growAlice</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playbackRate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Con un toque o un click, Alicia crecerá.</span>\ncake<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mousedown\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> growAlice<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ncake<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"touchstart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> growAlice<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>En otro ejemplo,&nbsp; <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/PNGGaV?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Red Queen's Race Game</a>, Alicia y La Reina Roja están ralentizandose constantemente:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">setInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Asegúrate de que la velocidad de reproducción nunca descienda por debajo de .4</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>redQueen_alice<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playbackRate <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">.4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    redQueen_alice<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playbackRate <span class=\"token operator\">*=</span> <span class=\"token number\">.9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"es\"><span>Pero hacer click o hacer tapping(pasar el puntero) sobre ellos hace que aceleren multiplicando su</span></span> <code>playbackRate</code>(velocidad de reproducción):</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">goFaster</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  redQueen_alice<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playbackRate <span class=\"token operator\">*=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1.1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> goFaster<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"touchstart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> goFaster<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"<span class=\"highlight-span\">Especificaciones</span>","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-playbackrate\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'Animation.playbackRate' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"Especificaciones"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.playbackRate","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Ejemplos","id":"ejemplos"},{"text":"<span class=\"highlight-span\">Especificaciones</span>","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"La propiedad Animation.playbackRate de la Web Animations API devuelve o  establece la velocidad de reproducción de la animación.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.playbackRate","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/playbackrate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/playbackrate/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate","title":"Animation.playbackRate"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.playbackRate - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}